Help on skill: tremendous blow
Skill type: offensive
Usage duration: quite long time
Affecting stats: Str/Dex/Weapon/Con

A skilled veteran can focus all his physical might behind one
massive destructive blow. Weaker opponents cannot survive this
brutal and terrible hit.
When used in berserk the damage is increased if used also in
middle of fight the damage is increased even further.
Your weapon skill and your knowledge on skill 'strike' affect
the damage done.
Masters in offensive manouvers might even complete the blow
a bit quicker than normal.
You need a weapon in your right hand to perform this skill.

